name: put my body back together
description:
Hey! This project is still in development--I'm still trying to figure out how to get the inventory to work the way I want it to.

This is a project made for the 170 series at UCSC. These confessions are all genuine, and were sourced completely anonymously. I hope you enjoy this early build!

Instructions: 

Z - interact

X -cancel/ make text faster 

Enter - Open the menu/start the game
